'''Hunvicko''' was a subsidiary of the [[InterGalactic Banking Clan]] that went bankrupt during the [[Clone Wars]].<ref name="Episode Guide" />

==Behind the scenes==
Hunvicko was first mentioned under the name Huvicko in the [[2003]] [[Star Wars Legends|''Star Wars'' Legends]] sourcebook ''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''.<ref name="Coruscant and the Core Worlds">''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''</ref> It was established to be [[canon]] by "[[An Old Friend]]," the fifth episode of the canon animated series ''[[Star Wars: The Clone Wars]]''' [[The Clone Wars: The Lost Missions|sixth season]].<ref name="An Old Friend">{{TCW|An Old Friend}}</ref>

